{"article_id":"2MtDvDSHgmBd2Xkj","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Russia will develop missiles","depth":8},{"id":1,"text":"banned under a Cold War agreement","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"if the US exits the pact ,","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"President Vladimir Putin has warned .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"His comments follow Nato 's accusation on Tuesday","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"that Russia has already broken the Intermediate-range Nuclear Forces","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"( INF )","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"Treaty .","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"Signed in 1987 by the US and USSR ,","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"it banned both countries ' use of all short and medium-range missiles .","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"But Mr Putin says","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"the accusation is a pretext","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"for the US to leave the pact .","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"In televised comments , the Russian leader said","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"many other countries had developed weapons","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"banned under the INF treaty .","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"`` Now it seems our American partners believe","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"that the situation has changed so much","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"that [ they ] must also have such a weapon , ''","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"he said .","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"`` What 's our response ?","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"It 's simple","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"- in that case we will also do this . ''","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"US President Donald Trump has previously said","depth":4},{"id":24,"text":"the country would leave the treaty","depth":5},{"id":25,"text":"because of Russian actions .","depth":5},{"id":26,"text":"Analysts say","depth":4},{"id":27,"text":"Russia sees the weapons as a cheaper alternative to conventional forces .","depth":4},{"id":28,"text":"Arriving for talks with Nato foreign ministers ,","depth":5},{"id":29,"text":"EU foreign affairs chief Federica Mogherini urged","depth":5},{"id":30,"text":"the two countries to save the treaty ,","depth":5},{"id":31,"text":"saying","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"it had `` guaranteed peace and security in European territory for 30 years now '' .","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"On Tuesday , the Western military alliance formally accused Russia of breaking the treaty .","depth":5},{"id":34,"text":"`` Allies have concluded","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"that Russia has developed and fielded a missile system , the 9M729 ,","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"which violates the INF Treaty","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"and poses significant risks to Euro-Atlantic security , ''","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"the Nato foreign ministers ' statement read .","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"The statement said","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"the member nations `` strongly support '' the US claim","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"that Russia is in breach of the pact ,","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"and called on Moscow to `` return urgently to full and verifiable compliance '' .","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"Speak","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"ng after the release of Nato 's statement ,","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"S Secretary of State Mike Pompeo said","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"ussia had 60 days to return to compliance with the treaty ,","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"fter which time the US would suspend its own compliance .","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"` During this 60 days we will still not test or produce or deploy any systems ,","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"nd we 'll see what happens during this 60-day period , ''","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"e said .","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"igned by the US and the USSR in 1987 ,","depth":5},{"id":52,"text":"he arms control deal banned all nuclear and non-nuclear missiles with short and medium ranges , except sea-launched weapons","depth":5},{"id":53,"text":"he US had been concerned by the Soviet deployment of the SS-20 missile system","depth":5},{"id":54,"text":"nd responded","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"y placing Pershing and cruise missiles in Europe","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"sparking widespread protests","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"n 2007 , Russian President Vladimir Putin declared","depth":5},{"id":58,"text":"he treaty no longer served Russia 's interests","depth":5},{"id":59,"text":"he move came","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"fter the US withdrew from the Anti-Ballistic Missile Treaty in 2002","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"n 2014 , then US President Barack Obama accused Russia of breaching the INF Treaty","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"fter it allegedly tested a ground-launched cruise missile .","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"e reportedly chose not to withdraw from the treaty under pressure from European leaders ,","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"ho said","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"uch a move could restart an arms race .","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"he last time","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"he US withdrew from a major arms treaty","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"as in 2002 ,","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"hen President George W Bush pulled the US out of the Anti-Ballistic Missile Treaty ,","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"hich banned weapons","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"esigned to counter ballistic nuclear missiles .","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"is administration 's move","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"o set up a missile shield in Europe","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"larmed the Kremlin ,","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"nd was scrapped by the Obama administration in 2009 .","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"t was replaced by a modified defence system in 2016 .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":153,"left":104,"right":152,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":99,"right":103,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":89,"right":98,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":89,"left":86,"right":88,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":86,"left":80,"right":85,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":80,"left":79,"right":3,"relatio